OverlaysShareTweetPreviousNextPreviousNext

Howard Marten Company has the capability of designing and building control panels to meet any customer specifications, for any part of the world.  From basic local operator panels to full logic control panels, all design, wiring, programming and testing are done in-house.
Some common examples of the controls that accompany our pumping skids are:

Local operator panels
Contactor and motor starter panels
Variable frequency drive air cooler control panels
Mechanical relay logic panels
PLC logic panels
HMI touchscreen user interface

Compliance with the standards, codes and regulations of foreign jurisdictions, or with specific industry requirements is familiar territory, as a global supplier of custom manufactured products to all major industries.  CSA, UL, IEC, FM, ATEX for mining, nuclear, petro-chemical, offshore etc. are among the many requirements regularly accommodated in our product designs.










